    <h1>Spicy Masala Maggi</h1>
    <p>This quick and flavorful noodle recipe is perfect for late-night cravings or a cozy snack.</p>

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>1 packet Maggi noodles</li>
      <li>1 cup water</li>
      <li>1 chopped green chili</li>
      <li>1/4 tsp turmeric powder</li>
      <li>1/2 tsp garam masala</li>
      <li>1 tbsp chopped coriander leaves</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Boil water in a pan and add the Maggi noodles.</li>
      <li>Add the tastemaker and stir well.</li>
      <li>Mix in green chili, turmeric, and garam masala.</li>
      <li>Cook for 2â€“3 minutes until noodles are soft and spices are absorbed.</li>
      <li>Garnish with coriander leaves and serve hot.</li>
    </ol>

